  <name>System Companion</name>
  <summary>System health and maintenance dashboard</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      System Companion is a fast, optimized, and beautiful system health &amp; maintenance 
      dashboard for Ubuntu Linux. It consolidates scattered system monitoring and 
      maintenance tools into a single, modern interface.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time system health monitoring</li>
      <li>Predictive maintenance alerts</li>
      <li>Intelligent cleanup recommendations</li>
      <li>Performance optimization tools</li>
      <li>Security and privacy monitoring</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
